CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 10, 1954, page 21, reads: "West Side - Space in the church was filled by deeply concerned residents."
TitMainTitle: Audience of men, women, and children, gathered for a police brutality meeting in the west section of the Bethel AME Church on Webster Avenue in the Hill District
